snippet.title: Out For Delivery teaser trailer
snippet.description:
https://out-for-delivery.com
A 360-degree interactive documentary following a food delivery courier in the rapid urbanizing Beijing. It was shot on January 23, 2020, the day before Lunar New Year's Eve and the same day Wuhan shut down due to COVID-19.
